Package com.restfb.types.instagram

Contains all types that are necessary to interact with the Instagram Graph API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IgComment
    Represents a Instagram Comment object
    IgContentPublishingLimit
    return type of the content publishing limit endpoint
    IgContentPublishingLimit.Config  
    IgFrom  
    IgHashtag
    Represents a Instagram Hashtag object
    IgMedia
    Represents the instagram media type
    IgMediaChild  
    IgUser
    Represents the instagram user type used in the Graph API
    IgUserProfile
    Respresents the Instagram User Profile object as defined here
